title: 215: Weight loss struggle, eating donuts & Pop Tarts, training to failure & MORE
description: Thanks to all of you who submitted questions this week. They flooded in! In this Q&A Sal, Adam & Justin answer your questions about unconventional training (indian clubs, kettle bells, etc), getting certified for personal benefit, eating donuts & Pop Tarts AND staying ripped, cutting calories but not losing weight and why you should not train to failure. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
